        "title": "Add narrated audio player for blog posts",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Add narrated audio for all current blog posts.\n- Add a custom full-width blog audio player with native waveform rendering, seek support, speed control, hover previews, and current section labels.\n- Add generated waveform metadata alongside the MP3 assets and a helper script to regenerate waveforms from the audio files.\n\n## Screenshots\n\n### Narrow view\n\n![Narrow view](https://flint-comet-2gbd.here.now/droppie-2026-06-02T21-55-12Z.png)\n\n### Desktop view\n\n![Desktop view](https://ivory-fable-xak6.here.now/droppie-2026-06-02T21-56-02Z.png)\n\n### Hover detail showing the heading tooltip\n\n![Hover detail showing the heading tooltip](https://quartz-canyon-fbq5.here.now/droppie-2026-06-02T21-56-26Z.png)\n\n### Hover detail showing preview progress\n\n![Hover detail showing preview progress](https://dusty-garden-a5ww.here.now/droppie-2026-06-02T21-57-00Z.png)\n\n### Player progress with current heading\n\n![Player progress with current heading](https://swift-quiche-92y2.here.now/droppie-2026-06-02T21-57-21Z.png)\n\n## Verification\n\n- `bun test`\n- `bun run test:built-assets`\n- `git diff --check`\n- Verified 9 MP3 files and 9 waveform JSON files; every waveform has version 1, 260 finite peaks, and values in range 0..1.\n",
